<item>
            <title>[LU-8400] Remove OBD_IOC_GET_MNTOPT ioctl as it&apos;s only used to pass info between mdd and mdt</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8400</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The OBD_IOC_GET_MNTOPT ioctl should be removed because it&apos;s not actually usable in user-space and is only used by kernel in mdd and mdt to pass information.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
